'''中美洲移民大篷车'''<ref>{{cite news|last1=Carcamo|first1=Cindy|last2=Repard|first2=Pauline|title=People 'associated with' Central American caravan have entered U.S. illegally, federal officials say|url=http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-sd-caravan-20180428-story.html|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2018-04-29|access-date=2018-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181019025528/http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-sd-caravan-20180428-story.html|archive-date=2018-10-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>是指从[[危地马拉|危地马拉]]-[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]边境前往[[美墨邊界|美墨邊界]]的由移民組成的[[大篷车|大篷车]]。這些移民乘坐大篷車前往美國。其中规模最大、最著名的是由{{en-link|无国界村组织|Pueblo Sin Fronteras}}在2017年初和2018年[[圣周|圣周]]期间从[[危地馬拉|危地馬拉]]、[[宏都拉斯|宏都拉斯]]和[[薩爾瓦多|薩爾瓦多]]組織出发的移民大篷車。

不過對於大篷车上的移民身份，到底是由寻求庇护的难民组成，还是仅仅是普通移民，分析人士存在着一些分歧。许多人权组织發現，中美洲国家暴力和虐待行為持續增加<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.unrefugees.org/emergencies/central-america/|title=Why People Are Fleeing Honduras & Guatemala - Central American Refugee Crisis|website=www.unrefugees.org|access-date=2019-05-19|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203195314/https://www.unrefugees.org/emergencies/central-america/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.unhcr.org/publications/operations/5630f24c6/women-run.html|title=Women on the Run|last=Refugees|first=United Nations High Commissioner for|website=UNHCR|language=en|access-date=2019-05-19|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114211229/https://www.unhcr.org/publications/operations/5630f24c6/women-run.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2018/06/central-america-border-immigration/563744/|title=Today's Migrant Flow Is Different|last=Martínez|first=Sofía|date=2018-06-26|website=The Atlantic|language=en-US|access-date=2019-05-19|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207141948/https://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2018/06/central-america-border-immigration/563744/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.futurity.org/central-american-migrants-1872742/|title=Violence at home pushes Central American migrants to U.S.|date=2018-09-24|website=Futurity|language=en-US|access-date=2019-05-19|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122015709/https://www.futurity.org/central-american-migrants-1872742/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。[[大赦国际|大赦国际]]援引《武装暴力与发展问题日内瓦宣言》（Geneva Declaration on Armed Violence and Development）的一份报告指出，2007年至2012年，中美洲的一些国家的女性年均杀人率居世界之首，與此同時全世界則是男性年均杀人率更高<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.amnestyusa.org/fleeing-for-our-lives-central-american-migrant-crisis/|title=Fleeing for Our Lives: Central American Migrant Crisis|date=2016-04-01|website=Amnesty International USA|language=en-US|access-date=2019-05-19|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122014829/https://www.amnestyusa.org/fleeing-for-our-lives-central-american-migrant-crisis/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Global Burden of Armed Violence |url=http://www.genevadeclaration.org/measurability/global-burden-of-armed-violence/global-burden-of-armed-violence-2015.html |website=Geneva Declaration on Armed Violence and Development |access-date=2019-05-23 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202023541/http://www.genevadeclaration.org/measurability/global-burden-of-armed-violence/global-burden-of-armed-violence-2015.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其他學者对大篷车人口构成的研究表明，大篷车上的人口更类似于普通的移民<<ref name="CREATE">{{cite news |last1=Dinan |first1=Stephen |title=Caravan mostly standard illegal immigrants, not refugees fleeing violence |url=https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2018/nov/28/migrant-caravan-mostly-standard-illegal-immigrants/ |access-date=2019-03-31 |agency=The Washington Times |date=2018-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331192140/https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2018/nov/28/migrant-caravan-mostly-standard-illegal-immigrants/ |archive-date=2019-03-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

